(274, '09 Tell us about your contacts - NO', '09-tell-us-about-your-contacts-no274', NULL, '\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-1\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-full\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"govuk-back-link ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px;\">Back</a></div></div><div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-2\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-two-thirds activearea\"><h1 class=\"govuk-heading-xl ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Tell us about your contacts</h1><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">It is really important that we identify the people you have been in close contact with beginning 48 hours before you first felt unwell so that we can contact them and tell them what they need to do to prevent further spread of the virus.</p><p class=\"ui-sortable-handle\"></p><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"p1 govuk-!-margin-bottom-6 govuk-!-margin-bottom-7 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">This might include either a work or home environment.</p><p class=\"ui-sortable-handle\"></p><h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Who have you been close to?</h2><div class=\"govuk-form-group ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">\n  <fieldset class=\"govuk-fieldset\" aria-describedby=\"changed-name-hint\">\n    \n    <label class=\"govuk-label\" for=\"event-name\">Have you been in face-to-face contact ( Less than 2 meters or 6 and a half feet) with someone 