n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </fieldset>\n</div><div class=\"govuk-form-group ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">\n  <fieldset class=\"govuk-fieldset\" aria-describedby=\"changed-name-hint\">\n    \n    <label class=\"govuk-label\" for=\"event-name\">Is this person under 18?</label>\n    <div class=\"govuk-radios govuk-radios--inline\">\n      <div class=\"govuk-radios__item\">\n        <input class=\"govuk-radios__input\" id=\"changed-name\" name=\"changed-name\" type=\"radio\" value=\"yes\">\n        <label class=\"govuk-label govuk-radios__label\" for=\"changed-name\">\n          Yes\n        </label>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"govuk-radios__item\">\n        <input class=\"govuk-radios__input\" id=\"changed-name-2\" name=\"changed-name\" type=\"radio\" value=\"no\">\n        <label class=\"govuk-label govuk-radios__label\" for=\"changed-name-2\">\n          No\n        </label>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </fieldset>\n</div><div class=\"govuk-form-group ui-sortable-handle\"><span id=\"changed-name-hint\" class=\"govuk-hint\"><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(90, 100, 104);\"></p></span></div><a href=\"10-tell-us-about-contacts275\" class=\"govuk-button ui-sortable-handle selected\" style=\"position: relative; left: 0px; top: 2px;\">Save and continue</a></div><div id=\"area-3\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-one-third\"></div></div>                        ', '2020-05-20 15:25:22'),
(275, '10 Tell us about contacts', '10-tell-us-about-contacts275', NULL, '\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-1\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-full\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"govuk-back-link ui-sortable-handle\">Back</a></div></div><div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-2\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-two-thirds activearea\"><h1 class=\"govuk-heading-xl ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Tell us about your contacts</h1><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">It is really important that we identify the people you have been in close contact with beginning 48 hours before you first felt unwell so that we can contact them and tell them what they need to do to prevent further spread of the virus.</p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">This might include either a work or home environment.</p><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"ui-sortable-handle\"></p><h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Who have you been close to?</h2><div class=\"govuk-form-group ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">\n  <fieldset class=\"govuk-fieldset\" aria-describedby=\"changed-name-hint\">\n    \n    <label class=\"govuk-label\" for=\"event-name\">Have you been in face-to-face contact (less than two meters or six and a half feet) with someone for longer than fifteen minutes?</label>\n    <div class=\"govuk-radios govuk-radios--inline\">\n      <div class=\"govuk-radios__item\">\n        <input class=\"govuk-radios__input\" id=\"changed-name\" name=\"changed-name\" type=\"radio\" value=\"yes\">\n        <label class=\"govuk-label govuk-radios__label\" for=\"changed-name\">\n          Yes\n        </label>\n 