(276, '11 Other contacts', '11-other-contacts276', NULL, '\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n      <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-1\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-full\"><a href=\"10-tell-us-about-contacts275\" class=\"govuk-back-link ui-sortable-handle\">Back</a></div></div><div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-2\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-two-thirds activearea\"><h1 class=\"govuk-heading-xl ui-sortable-handle selected\" style=\"\">Other situations you might have been in contact with other people</h1><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"govuk-body  govuk-!-margin-bottom-5 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">There might be other situations where you have been in contact with people for an extended piece of time where you might not know their details but it would still be helpful if you can provide us with any details you can remember.</p><p class=\"ui-sortable-handle\"></p><p class=\"ui-sortable-handle\"></p><h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Possible situations</h2><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\"></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">Have you been in contact with someone in any of these scenarios (or similar) 48 hours before you fel