(295, '11 0 Other situations you might have been in contact with other people', '11-0-other-situations-you-might-have-been-in-contact-with-other-people295', NULL, '\n      \n      <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-1\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-full\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"govuk-back-link\">Back</a></div></div><div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-2\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-two-thirds activearea\"><h1 class=\"govuk-heading-xl\" style=\"\">Other situations you might have been in contact with other people</h1><p class=\"govuk-body\"><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">There might be other situations where you have been in contact with people for an extended piece of time where you might not know their details but it would still be helpful if you can provide us with any details you can remember.</p></p><h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" style=\"\">Possible situations</h2><p class=\"govuk-body\"><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">Have you been in contact with somone in any of these scenarios (or similar) 48 hours before you felt unwell or received a positive test result?<br></p></p><p class=\"govuk-body\"><ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">A group of unidentified people (example lecture, public transport, other people you don’t know)</span></li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">Deceased contact</span></li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">Contact in ICU</span></li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">A nursing home or a health / social care setting where a confirmed case is a patient / resident / member of staff</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">Contacts outside of Northern Ireland</li></ul></p><div class=\"govuk-radios govuk-radios--inline\">\n      <div class=\"govuk-radios__item\">\n        <input class=\"govuk-radios__input\" id=\"changed-name\" name=\"changed-name\" type=\"radio\" value=\"yes\">\n        <label class=\"govuk-label govuk-radios__label\" for=\"changed-name\">\n          Yes\n        </label>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"govuk-radios__item govuk-!-margin-bottom-7\">\n        <input class=\"govuk-radios__input govuk-!-margin-bottom-7\" id=\"changed-name-2\" name=\"changed-name\" type=\"radio\" value=\"no\">\n        <label class=\"govuk-label govuk-radios__label\" for=\"changed-name-2\">\n          No\n        </label>\n      </div></div><a href