(296, 'Confirmation page', 'confirmation-page296', NULL, '\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-1\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-full activearea\"><div class=\"govuk-panel govuk-panel--confirmation\">\n  <h1 class=\"govuk-panel__title\">\nInformation received\n </h1>\n  <div class=\"govuk-panel__body\">\n    <strong>Thank you</strong>\n  </div>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"govuk-grid-row\"><div id=\"area-2\" class=\"sortablelist connectedSortable ui-sortable govuk-grid-column-two-thirds\"><h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\">Thank you for helping us learn about the virus</h2><p class=\"govuk-body ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"\"></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">By giving us these details you are helping us learn about the virus and<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">contributing to our efforts to save lives and get back to normal.</p><p class=\"p2 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); min-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">The information you have given us will not be used for any other purposes</p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">or shared outside of this…..</p><p class=\"p2 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); min-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">If you have any further questions about this process please<br><br>got to <span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 52, 98);\">https://covid-19.hscni.net/</span></p><p class=\"p2 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); min-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">or contact us on…….</p><p class=\"p2 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); min-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p class=\"p1 ui-sortable-handle\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\">f you haven’t started to self-isolate yet your isolation period began when you received your result and lasts for 7 days. <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p2 ui